This module wraps oceansoft/alb/aws (app.terraform.io/oceansoft/alb/aws).
Derived from terraform-aws-modules/terraform-aws-alb (Apache-2.0).
Original author: Anton Babenko

Value-add by nnthanh101@gmail.com (oceansoft.io):
- ADLC governance integration (FOCUS 1.2+ tags, CPS 234 compliance defaults)
- TLS 1.3 enforcement via default listener configuration
- Simplified interface for BC1/BC2/BC3 business cases
- CloudFront, WAF, DNS optional integration
